About
-----
This plugin for OJS 2 provides an import/export plugin to generate metadata information for 
issues for indexing in Elibrary. Generated reports sending by Articulus (http://e-library.ru/projects/articulus/Portfolio.aspx).
Official website of Russian library is hosted here www.elibrary.ru.
Contract system is here http://elibrary.ru/projects/contracts/publisher/messages/messages.asp.

License
-------
This plugin is licensed under the GNU General Public License v2. See the file COPYING for the 
complete terms of this license.

System Requirements
-------------------
Same requirements as the OJS 2.x core.

Installation
------------
To install the plugin:
 - copy the vinnipoohPlugin folder into OJS/plugins/importexport

The export functionality can then be accessed through: 
 - Home > User > Journal Management > Import/Export Data > vinnipoohPlugin

